manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/bin/daemon/main.rs"
name = "trade-noded"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[package]
name = "trade-node"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
atty = "0.2"
colored = "2.0.0"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
envy = "0.4"
opentelemetry = "0.17.0"
opentelemetry-jaeger = "0.16.0"
tracing = "0.1.34"
tracing-core = "0.1.26"
tracing-opentelemetry = "0.17.2"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3.11"

[dependencies.pyo3]
version = "0.16.4"
features = ["auto-initialize"]
optional = false

[dependencies.rustls]
version = "0.20.5"
features = ["dangerous_configuration"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.137"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.18.1"
features = ["full"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-futures]
version = "0.2.5"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.trade-core]
path = "../trade-core"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.trade-protocol]
path = "../trade-protocol"
features = []
optional = false

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "trade_node"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
